   "source": [
    "#### 3.\tEst ce qu’il y a une relation significative entre le sexe et la méthode d’entraînement?\n",
    "- On applique le test de kh-deux et on vérifie ses conditions d'application"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "751a101c-9c22-41d2-a4b2-017daeb6e7c3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "tab = pd.crosstab(df[\"SEXE\"], df[\"METHODE_ENTRAINEMENT\"])\n",
    "chi2, p, dof, expected = stats.chi2_contingency(tab)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "aca6d1f6-ac16-4ebc-be4c-7d74c4d9ca6f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Afficher les effectifs théoriques:\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(3,3))\n",
    "sns.heatmap(expected,annot=True)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "96912d41-b469-4590-b5db-a7e281c518f7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "N.B: tous les effectifs théoriques > 5"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "5bd6c077-9912-4f81-ac5b-ee986826a176",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "## afficher la p-value\n",
    "print(p.round(3))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "fb7bc3f3-1fcb-48c8-bdb2-ef248f4f7799",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "N.B comme $p-value>0.05$ alors il n'y a pas de reltion significative entre les deux variables!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "c8004f3f-76b5-4a67-a977-ab09e4afe434",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Taill de l'effet en cas d'une relation significative: V de Cramér \n",
    "n = tab.to_numpy().sum()\n",
    "r, k = tab.shape\n",
    "cramers_v = np.sqrt(chi2 / (n * (min(r-1, k-1))))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(cramers_v.round(3))"
   ]
  },
